<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18700</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>星期六早上，乔伊坐在桌子前写发表。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她正在网上读一篇叫做《做朋友》的文章。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是现在，她关上了妈妈的笔记本电脑，坐在那里思考。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在想什么呢？” 爷爷问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊抬头看着爷爷微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有一个好主意。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我马上就回来！” 乔伊跑出厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她回来时，她抱着一堆美术用品。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呼！” 乔伊边说边把所有的东西扔到了餐桌上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要做什么？” 爷爷问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿着一个大勺子在燃气灶上的锅里搅着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的特别发明！” 乔伊笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先，她从纸板上剪下了一个桨形。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她用黑纸剪出了一个指针。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把指针固定在纸板上后，转了几下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太完美了！” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷尝了一口锅里的汤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“放一点盐的话，这个鸡汤也会很完美的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91474</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不知道凯蒂会不会按时回家吃午饭。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊在纸板上画了两个大圆点，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个用的是绿色马克笔，一个用的是红色马克笔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她在绿圆点上画了一张笑脸，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在红圆点上画了一张哭脸，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>又在纸板边上画上了蓝色的波浪线。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿起自己的作品欣赏着。“画完了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“午饭也做好了！” 爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他给乔伊盛了一碗汤放在桌上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着乔伊的发明，挠了挠头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看起来很好，不过......这是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一个友谊测定仪！” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138681</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用大拇指把指针转向绿圆点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它在笑，因为爷爷您是最好的朋友！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，乔伊看了看钟表。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要收拾东西了。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快到一点了，差不多快到方块舞的排练时间了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂正在柳树溪图书馆写她的发表。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她找到了两本书，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一本是《弯曲和伸展》，另一本是《快乐健身》。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“戴格斯特叔叔，肌肉可真有趣。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>戴格斯特叔叔是星期六的图书馆管理员。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道人们伸舌头需要一块特殊的肌肉吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182749</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂对戴格斯特叔叔伸出了舌头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>戴格斯特动了动眼镜，看着凯蒂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“确实有趣。” 戴格斯特叔叔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他继续翻找图书馆的音乐光盘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“找到了！” 他说道，“《方块舞音乐与学习指南》！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太棒了！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她打开了光盘盒，看了看跳方块舞的说明书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要拿走它！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂把所有东西都放进了她的背包，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后看了一眼手表。该走了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“戴格斯特叔叔，谢谢您的帮助。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完，凯蒂转过了身。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚正站在她身后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ALOHA！你好！” 奥利维亚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ALOHA！再见！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她是谁？” 戴格斯特叔叔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她是奥利维亚。” 凯蒂说，“她也是四年级。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，戴格斯特叔叔桌子上的电话响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起。” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂，你带奥利维亚参观一下图书馆。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是......” 凯蒂说，“我得回家，我......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267107</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>戴格斯特叔叔没有在听，他已经在忙着通电话了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂, 太好了！” 奥利维亚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要是能帮我写关于皮肤的发表就好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看来 ‘聪明小姐’ 需要帮助了。” 凯蒂想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道要保持皮肤干净，防止日晒。” 奥利维亚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，那还不够写成一篇完整的发表。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂挑了一下眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不准备谈谈毒藤或蜱虫吗？” 她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蜱虫？那是什么？” 奥利维亚问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂喜欢给人们讲蜱虫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你确实是需要帮助啊！” 她叹了口气说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许我们应该坐下来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>